"8661":{
"Text":"CALL statement\r\n\r\nEffectively performs a JSR to the specified address, with the following register contents:\r\n\r\n  (A,Y) = call address\r\n  X-reg = $9D\r\n\r\nThe called routine can return with RTS, and Applesoft will continue with the next statement.\r\n",
